 models with observations of 4 Be stars that exhibited long-term\npolarimetric activity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Feb 2014 17:31:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 27 Feb 2014 09:56:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-18"}
