ion with\nsegmental spectrum area were 6.00%, 0.75, 3.77%, and 15.40%, respectively,\nshowing an overwhelming improvement.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Feb 2014 08:05:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-02-11"}
